title: Land Use Committee Meets Tues., Oct. 20 (ERNC - Eagle Rock Neighborhood Council)
text: ( Source : ERNC - Eagle Rock Neighborhood Council ) The next meeting of the Land Use and Planning Committee (LUPC) of the ERNC is on Tuesday evening, October 20 , 2015 , at 7:00 pm at Eagle Rock City Hall , 2035 Colorado Blvd, Los Angeles, CA
